1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:08,360
We beseech the Medicine God to capture the Plague Boy.

3
00:01:09,160 --> 00:01:10,720
Legend has it that many years ago,

4
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:12,760
the Plague Boy possessed children

5
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,000
and spread pestilence.

6
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,480
The people had to ask the Medicine God to suppress him.

7
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,000
Run!

8
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:38,280
Run!

9
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:43,720
I thought this place was lively enough,

10
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:45,240
so I wanted to come and sell my new products.

11
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:46,240
But what does she do?

12
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,170
She scared all the customers away.

13
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,759
Stop it!

14
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,780
You can't touch this Temple of the Medicine God.

15
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,720
Without the Medicine God to suppress the Plague Boy,

16
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,840
the plague will strike again!

17
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,370
What are you yelling about?

18
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,960
Where did this old geezer come from,

19
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,360
trying to boss us around?

20
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:10,440
Offending the Medicine God will bring retribution!

21
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,080
If you want to worship,

22
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,360
go worship your Medicine God.

23
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,720
I'll send you to the afterlife to worship him!

24
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,440
Get him!

25
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:25,740
Beat him up!

26
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:26,840
Stop!

27
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,420
What are you doing?

28
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,079
Sir.

29
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,760
What's all the noise?

30
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,440
Your Excellency.

31
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:41,040
Thanks to the protection of the God of Medicine,

32
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,640
the plague was driven away.

33
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,079
If he's gone,

34
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,700
who will the people nearby

35
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,880
rely on for protection?

36
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,040
The plague

37
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,079
has been gone for so many years.

38
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,240
It's time

39
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,600
This person has a strange aura.

40
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:01,000
to worship the sage to bless us with wealth.

41
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:03,240
You are just a minor constable,

42
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:06,420
yet you dare to interfere with the Duke of Jia's estate.

43
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,720
How bold of you.

44
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,680
The Duke of Jia's estate?

45
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,490
Since you know of the Duke of Jia's estate,

46
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,880
then get lost.

47
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,680
Although I recently started working at Yingtian Prefecture,

48
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,640
I also know

49
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,040
that this Medicine God Temple

50
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,840
was funded and built by the local people.

51
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,440
It doesn't belong to anyone.

52
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,840
There is nothing the Duke of Jia's estate wants

53
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,480
that it cannot get.

54
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:41,079
Greetings, Princess.

55
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,240
How dare you not kneel before me.

56
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,440
Your Highness.

57
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:52,240
The Medicine God Temple belongs to the people here.

58
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,840
Even the Duke of Jia's Estate

59
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:56,370
cannot ignore the law and forcibly occupy it.

60
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,680
How bold!

61
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,200
This land

62
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:02,140
already belongs to our Chamber of Commerce.

63
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,100
You slander the royal family.

64
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,480
What should be your punishment?

65
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:07,280
Is that so?

66
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:10,320
Do you have any documents for me to review?

67
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,080
If not,

68
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,080
it's forced occupation.

69
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,040
As a constable,

70
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:14,500
I have the right to stop it.

71
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,480
My uncle is not feeling well.

72
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,010
Send him back to rest first.

73
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,040
I really appreciate

74
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,440
the courage of a little constable like you.

75
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,300
I won't hold it against you today.

76
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,720
I will immediately order the yamen

77
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,040
to issue the deed for this place.

78
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,450
When the time comes,

79
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,360
I want you

80
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:43,580
to deliver it to the Duke's mansion personally.

81
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,360
I really like what he made.

82
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,960
Take him back with us as well.

83
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,440
Wait a minute.

84
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,300
What are you doing?

85
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,440
There is nothing I want

86
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,920
that I cannot get.

87
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,640
Whoever dares to stop me,

88
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:09,240
watch your head.

89
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,840
Are you crazy?

90
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:12,960
I will go with her.

91
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,520
The cooperation with Miss Chai last time

92
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,640
was ruined by you.

93
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,520
This time it's a big investor.

94
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,250
If I can get her investment,

95
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,580
wouldn't my business take off immediately?

96
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,730
You have nothing to say now, right?

97
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:26,400
Let's go.

98
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,360
Mr. Liu.

99
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,380
Mr. Liu was taken away by them.

100
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,770
He wanted to go himself.

101
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,159
I couldn't care less.

102
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:46,680
From now on,

103
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,680
you will stay here

104
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,640
and make the candy you sell for me.

105
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,440
Cut the crap.

106
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,080
Take me to see your uncle.

107
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,320
Bastard!

108
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,159
How dare you refuse me!

109
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,080
Believe it or not,

110
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,520
I'll have you beheaded.

111
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,100
I'll ask you one more time.

112
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,570
Do you accept or not?

113
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,920
I'm telling you,

114
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,120
don't delay my business.

115
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,240
I'm an official.

116
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:05,970
An official?

117
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,320
I'm so scared.

118
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:14,040
You won't behave until I make a move.

119
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,840
I'm telling you, I don't hit women.

120
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,040
Come on, hit me.

121
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:19,640
Take this.

122
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,490
How dare you resist!

123
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,320
I'm telling you,

124
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,120
stop it right now,

125
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,920
or I'll have you beheaded.

126
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,160
You forced me.

127
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,680
You... you know acupressure?

128
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,500
What acupressure?

129
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,240
This is cutting off the blood flow

130
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,680
to temporarily paralyze your nerves.

131
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,840
Stop talking nonsense.

132
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,040
Take me to your uncle.

133
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,720
How dare you disrespect me!

134
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,960
I'll execute your entire family!

135
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,280
You're a stubborn girl.

136
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,680
I need to teach you a lesson.

137
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,560
Stop it!

138
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,760
I will just take you there.

139
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,080
This time,

140
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,440
we can make a fortune again.

141
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:11,840
Who?

142
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,840
Who is it?

143
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:29,640
Who is it?

144
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,680
Dry weather,

145
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,880
beware of fire.

146
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,880
Dry weather,

147
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:08,040
beware of fire.

148
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,610
Where is your uncle?

149
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,560
You played me.

150
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,760
So what if I did?

151
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,240
No one can threaten me.

152
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,640
I don't have time for your nonsense.

153
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,240
I'm telling you,

154
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,440
your uncle might be in danger right now.

155
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,760
Stop trying to scare me.

156
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,559
I always

157
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,320
pay back every little grudge.

158
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,640
Now I'll show you

159
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:45,960
what happens when you offend me.

160
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:48,160
Brat, I'm not kidding.

161
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:49,840
I'm not kidding either.

162
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,480
Watch how I punish you.

163
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,640
Princess Jianning.

164
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,920
I'll teach you to hit me!

165
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:57,800
I'll teach you to bully me.

166
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:58,400
Princess.

167
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,280
Your Highness, it's terrible.

168
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,480
Something happened at the chamber of commerce.

169
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,480
Your uncle...

170
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,080
The Princess's uncle came to the chamber to discuss business.

171
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,160
He suddenly attacked people with a knife.

172
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,440
The night watchman passed by

173
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,840
and quickly reported it.

174
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,320
What happened?

175
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,440
Uncle.

176
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,640
I told you something would happen.

177
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,640
If you had found out earlier,

178
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:22,240
none of this would have happened.

179
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,440
Why are you yelling at me?

180
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,280
I didn't know.

181
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,280
I've never seen him so angry.

182
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,360
Just compensate them.

183
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,890
Can you pay for a human life?

184
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,240
If I cut you and then compensate you,

185
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,080
would you be willing?

186
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,840
I...

187
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,460
Do you remember Master Tu?

188
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,500
When he had an episode,

189
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,290
he almost lost his mind,

190
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:52,090
even resorting to killing his own family.

191
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,440
You said

192
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,680
it was because something in his brain

193
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:56,760
affected his mind.

194
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,400
Could it be...

195
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:02,000
During the day, based on his symptoms,

196
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,600
I already had my suspicions.

197
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,540
I wanted to get closer to observe carefully.

198
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,930
So that was your reason.

199
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,940
You reported the case last night.

200
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,560
What was the situation at the scene?

201
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,480
Last night,

202
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,380
when I passed by the Chamber of Commerce,

203
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:46,120
I heard a commotion inside.

204
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:48,920
And,

205
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,840
when I passed by the God of Medicine Temple,

206
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,480
I also saw the Plague Boy.

207
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,720
It was terrifying.

208
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:59,600
The weather is dry.

209
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,920
Beware of fire.

210
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,320
It's terrifying.

211
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:32,520
Let's go.

212
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,160
Go.

213
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:40,960
Plague Boy.

214
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,040
Why do we always run into

215
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:47,200
such bad luck?

216
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,760
It's been ten years.

217
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:49,880
Just at this time,

218
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,680
Plague Boy has come out to make trouble again.

219
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,570
Plague Boy is just a legend.

220
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:58,700
We need to find clues from the Princess's uncle.

221
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,600
But,

222
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:05,040
I already let him go.

223
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,920
What?

224
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,200
Don't blame me.

225
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,320
The Duchess came to ask for him in person.

226
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,480
How dare I disobey?

227
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:57,680
He is my brother.

228
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,410
No matter what happens,

229
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,650
we must protect him.

230
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:01,720
Remember.

231
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,760
Word of today's events must not spread under any circumstances.
